message.raw:
Fixed issues from latest inline code comments in PR 2652.

Removed some `gzdbg`s, changed some to `gzmsg`.
Some asserts were transformed to `if`s.
Keyboard controls are now configurable (and optional).
Converted public methods in `TrackedVehiclePlugin` to protected.
Unit/integration tests still to be written.
